      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-secondary-200 dark:border-secondary-700">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-4 text-sm">
        <a href="/mentions" class="text-secondary-600 hover:text-primary-600 dark:text-secondary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-400">
          Mentions légales & Accessibilité
        </a>
        <span class="text-secondary-400 dark:text-secondary-600">•</span>
        <a href="/apropos" class="text-secondary-600 hover:text-primary-600 dark:text-secondary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-400">
